</div><h1 itemprop="headline" class="entry-title"><a href="//www.nytimes.com/politics/first-draft/2015/03/04/today-in-politics-108/" rel="bookmark" class="entry-title-link " title="Permanent link to Today in Politics">Today in Politics</a></h1>	<div class="hide-on-viewport-medium byline">
		<!-- date published --><time class="dateline " datetime="2015-03-04T12:13:45+00:00" itemprop="datePublished">7:13 <span class="seg">am ET</span></time>
			<!-- date updated --><span class="visually-hidden updated">7:13 <span class="seg">am ET</span></span>		<div class="name" data-author="By The New York Times" >
			<span class="author vcard" itemprop="author creator" itemtype="//schema.org/Person">
				By <address class="vcard first-byline" itemscope itemprop="author creator" itemtype="//schema.org/Person" itemid="The New York Times">
					<span class="fn" itemprop="name">The New York Times</span>
				</address>			</span>
